I have had worse than that tried on me, and have yet to go to the FoB to take out my vengeance <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p><b>Grimjaw Badflagon Retired</b> <i>"cosmopolitain"</i> <b>Thug.</b>
