</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/ugrimjawbadflagon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimjaw Badflagon</A> at: 10/10/01 12:40:32 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/uvelaelsoulrender.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Velael Soulrender</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tavern Regular</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 12:46:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4122.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My evening with the goods (and how dumb some lowbies can</span><hr size=1> You know Grim, you still are nuts. But I happen to agree with you a lot recently. Oh well, I must be going insane. Anyways, now that I have shown how much of a bluebie poon I am, back to playing SZ, and I SWEAR I will kill agrul before he greens out, that damn bard always escapes me, of finds me soloing and low on mana......so we never actually kill anything. I'll get you once Agrul <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><font color = ff0000>Velael regards you indifferently - He appears to be a taxi</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/usadadar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sadadar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>drunken' poon</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 1:03:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4122.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My evening with the goods (and how dumb some lowbies can</span><hr size=1> I remember when Kiluminati came to perma and said the same thing.<br>
<br>
I was messing around in king room with two of my friends, and had told him that we wouldn't bother him if he didn't bother low levels.<br>
<br>
About 30 minutes pass and I start hearing shouts about something, KSing or something like that, done by the wizzy. And I send him a tell, that's something along the lines of, sit invis somewhere and I have some guildies in zone, you'll get the item drop for your trade when it drops.<br>
<br>
Well some time passes by, he gets the item, he comes to king room, I presume to thank me, and nukes me.<br>
<br>
He dies in king room.<br>
<br>
He calls me all sorts of names.<br>
<br>
This is typical for what goods expect when people come to do the quests, get what you want, then kill all the greenies before you leave and XP lose them using trains and whatnot. It's shitty, but it happens.<br>
<br>
Next time, just go in force the first time, grab your item and head out, or go in, kill the mobs you need in a reclusive area, and then head out.<br>
<br>
It isn't too hard to zone in somewhere invis, walk to a camp that isn't taken, and use it. I do it in newt and evil controlled dungeons all the time. They rarely notice you unless there are a few mildly intelligent people in the zone, but we're on SZ, so it's rare.<br>
<br>
Sitting next to a group of goods is asking for it. You're facing severe death and destruction if they can bring it about. Like you said, we enjoy friendly competition, and if we ran by eachother in a zone when neither of us felt like PKing, we might toss a /bonk back and forth and head on. But if you were chillin in perma waiting for a quest item (or I was xping in DL <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :o --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/embarassed.gif ALT=":o"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) I'd come by and say high with a /cast 2 =)<br>
<br>
Course if you offered me two jacinths for a heart of frost, I'd have gone down with you and cleared the goods from the zone myself =)<br>
<br>
Sad <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub73.ezboard.com/uvelaelsoulrender.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Velael Soulrender</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Tavern Regular</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 1:08:25 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub73.ezboard.com/fsullonzektavernfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4122.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My evening with the goods (and how dumb some lowbies can</span><hr size=1> lol....yes, I'm a bluebie poon....I attacked Sadadar 2 on 6 <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
